<item>
            <title>[LU-3243] sanity.sh test_77i: algo set to crc32 instead of adler</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3243</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve just seen this test failure:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&apos;algo set to crc32 instead of adler&apos; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/eae87668-aee2-11e2-a8d0-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/eae87668-aee2-11e2-a8d0-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;against my patch:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3440&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,3440&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="18620">LU-3243</key>
            <summary>sanity.sh test_77i: algo set to crc32 instead of adler</summary>
